Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.87,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}現在的你 全力支持著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.62,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在的我 也有了支持你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:26.63,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使彷徨無助 我們也要結伴前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.75,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}奔向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.76,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然與朋友們嬉戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}這樣一路走來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻依然感到內心的空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.69,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受盡冷漠的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:51.86,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}寄身於時代的狂風中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:01:00.49,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}勇氣與不安 如影相隨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:08.38,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}因此 現在就要用我的雙手創造未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.55,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}那些讓我們受傷感到絕望的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.89,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些令我們哭泣感到難過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.85,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然縈繞於心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.85,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們終將跨過重重障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.11,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}以超越所有人為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.87,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}君が今僕を支えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.62,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕が今君を支える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:26.63,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから迷いながらも共に生きていこうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.75,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:38.76,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲間と戯れ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}それなりで居ても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:44.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もの足りなさを感じてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.69,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷めた目で見られて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:51.86,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}乾いた時代の風に吹かれている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:01:00.49,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}不安な心と勇気が背中合わせになっている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:08.38,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}だけど今なら夢をこの手で叶えてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.55,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}傷ついて壊れそうな日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.89,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙して困らせる日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.85,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:24.85,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕達はそれを越えていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.85,0:01:29.11,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}誰より上を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:49.06,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經幻想 夢中的幸福{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:56.02,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有人親手為我實現{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:21:03.08,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在繁忙的都市中尋找藉口{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:09.83,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們都在編織著美麗的謊言{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:17.39,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你這樣 真的滿足了嗎?」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:25.54,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在內心深處審視自己{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:29.26,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒能與你相遇{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:32.63,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只會強顏歡笑{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:39.70,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著虛偽的面具度過{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:43.45,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你眼中的堅定{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:46.67,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我逐漸改變{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:54.53,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了擺脫昨日飄浮不定的心緒…{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:49.06,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢に見ていたシアワセなら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:56.02,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かが運んでくれると思ってた{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:21:03.08,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急ぎ足の街で言い訳ばかり{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:09.83,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,みんなも同じとうそぶいてた{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:17.39,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「本当にキミはいま　満足してるの？」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:25.54,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心の真ん中見抜かれたようで{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:29.26,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたと出会えなかったら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:32.63,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偽った笑顔のまま{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:39.70,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,うわべの態度や言葉を繰り返したね{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:43.45,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの瞳の力で{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:46.67,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私は変わってゆこう{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:54.53,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日の揺らいた気持ちを脱ぎ捨てるために…{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【註釋】
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就  4·十四 「二間高掛」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:28.13,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「二間高掛」：在四線上相隔兩路掛角稱為二間高掛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.75,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,akira是日文「亮」的羅馬音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?  akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【對白】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.03,0:00:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安時代的棋師 藤原佐為
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越了遙遠的時空 在進藤光的心中復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了領悟「神之一手」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,zelda啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙可能是個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼人? 這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:01:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為 這傢伙的水平怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比至今為止遇到的任何人都要厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.90,0:02:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 這個人是職業棋手嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職業棋手是不會這麼頻繁地跟業餘棋手下棋的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是職業棋手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是職業棋手 那他是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是棋神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國際業餘圍棋大賽就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到了日本…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要到了日本…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許就能知道sai是何方神聖了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小孩!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很強… 可是 不是他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是sai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45}{\fnsimhei}{\bord2}{\i1}{\pos(415,382)}追憶之局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:58.49,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}{\3a&H1E&\3c&HFFFFFF&}第20屆國際業餘圍棋大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在網上下過圍棋嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想問sai嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…你就是sai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai也來了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是在說sai嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是sai吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 早上其他選手來問過我是不是sai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai究竟是什麼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還不知道他的真實身份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和sai下過棋?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他非常厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發信息問他到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他卻沒有回應
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來希望他也會來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個月前和他下過一局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是憑我的實力 完全不是他的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然沒和sai下過棋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我觀戰過他的對局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且經常看他下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和sai下過 大概在10天之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是這個暑假突然出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他太強了 關於他的傳聞迅速傳遍了整個網絡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界各地的人都慕名向他挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在問「who is sai?」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}我也和sai下過棋!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai  一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都在議論sai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請安靜點 還有人正在比賽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他究竟是什麼人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他絕對不是一個普通的棋手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在議論網上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網上?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說起來 剛才和谷也提到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒方老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 緒方老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼? 你認識島野?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他以前經常去名人學習班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天是來給他打氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮一會兒也會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這裏好像有點吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在議論著網上有個非常厲害的圍棋高手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自稱sai
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是中國的李臨新
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和sai下過棋 可是中盤就認輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他是哪個職業棋手嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai經常出現 而且不選擇對手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職業棋手怎麼會這麼有時間?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是韓國的選手 我姓金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有和sai下過棋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我來日本之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友職業棋手俞七段曾經聯繫過我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我剛剛和sai下過棋」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「到日本以後幫我問問sai是誰?」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因為sai絕對是日本的頂尖棋士」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 他應該不是職業棋手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他輸給過哪個人了嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他可能還會變得更強!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谷 你在這裏幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是你們在談論sai
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能置身事外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也和sai下過棋嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才不是說了嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個很厲害的傢伙 但不是職業棋手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說他啊 他就叫sai
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是森下老師的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個什麼樣的棋手?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說是什麼樣的棋手…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個月之前和他下過棋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起他的棋路 好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候讓我覺得他很像秀策…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀策?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本因坊秀策嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我經常練習秀策的棋譜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以總覺得他們的手法很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看起來就像秀策那樣厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且後來我又看過很多次他網上的對局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 看了很多局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙經常出現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我覺得他真是強得不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 每次看到他 就會發現他又變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的手法也漸漸改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像秀策學會了現代定式一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀策學會了現代定式?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣啊 佐為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只有我能看見你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是神嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在這個盒子裏 你是真實存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原佐為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是怪物?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本因坊秀策…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個隱藏在網上的本因坊秀策嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想向他挑戰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 怎麼覺得會場的氣氛有點怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不關你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮 你在網上下過圍棋嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和關西的職業棋手下過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說網上有個非常厲害的棋手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他看起來像個業餘棋手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是就連韓國的職業棋手也輸給了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網上的圍棋高手?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說了嘛 不關你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谷 你無緣無故生什麼氣啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那個人名字叫sai
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 雖然是我個人的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是sai可能是個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼這麼想?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 他從七月份開始就一直出現在網上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜一定是因為暑假的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他還給我發過信息說「我很強吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很孩子氣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼? 你和sai說過話?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們談過些什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只說過一次而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼頭緒嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你以為是他的話 那是你想錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的你 甚至讓我以為看到了「神之一手」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個可以上網
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs28}我們能看見sai嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai可能在網上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 中盤認輸 我們又贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為 和你一起大獲全勝的感覺真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個對手並不是很強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個盒子裏的確有很難對付的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:11:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一下子又跳出這麼多窗口要挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先拒絕掉 回到原來的窗口…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,akira
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,akira
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是塔矢嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又來了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 剛剛才拒絕了一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個接一個 沒完沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微鬆口氣怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免費給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you  三谷姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 我們又回到剛才那個窗口了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sai… 邀請我對局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他接受挑戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是塔矢的話那該有多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那麼想和你下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想讓他和你下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他不知道是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是可以滿足塔矢的願望的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們試試怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看他到底是不是塔矢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們怎麼做呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我選好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一手  17·四
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17·四…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白子下在了左上角的星位上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16·十七
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白子下在了「4·十七」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就下在「15·三」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒? 白子不走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在考慮什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在右下方掛角了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為 接下來呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迄今為止他走的棋步都和那時一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為 這是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 正是我殺得他慘敗的那局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我和他的第二次對局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那時的對局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 下一步  15·十六 「尖」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不走了難道不是因為他就是塔矢嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是因為他想起了上次的對局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以停手了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說塔矢發現對手是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道… 怎麼會!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他用的就是我們常說的「秀策尖」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了? 他怎麼不下了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又下在和那時同樣的位置上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐為 這樣不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他知道了對手是我們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在的對手那麼強嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜託你了 佐為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始不要下在和上次一樣的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道能不能騙過他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他到底是不是塔矢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒? 他在長考啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.55,0:16:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他認輸了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要認輸?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們繼續下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會影響整個比賽的進行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會要求對方改日再戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 改日再戰?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三谷姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明天在嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我明天要和幾個朋友出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個星期天才回來上班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你能不能幫我告訴這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「下個星期天上午10點…」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你應該學學自己發信息了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(436,156)\fnsimhei}{\fs20}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\1c&H000000&}希望能夠改日再戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,235)\fnsimhei}{\fs20}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\1c&H000000&}下個星期天 上午10點…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個星期天啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾 那時候我們已經回國了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(482,106)\fnsimhei}{\fs22}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\1c&H000000&}希望能夠改日再戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(345,183)\fnsimhei}{\fs22}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\1c&H000000&}下個星期天 上午10點…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(345,244)\fnsimhei}{\fs22}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\1c&H000000&}我接受對局
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他接受了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島野先生 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子究竟是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是日本頂尖棋士塔矢名人的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是sai為什麼會要求和他對局呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是啊  sai很少會主動要求別人對局的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個星期天再戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他居然毫不猶豫地接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是職業考試的第一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是即使輸了一場也無所謂!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:18:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和身份不明的對手下棋是不是更有趣!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}真是的 我們最終還是不知道sai的真實身份啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}如果有什麼關於sai的消息 請一定要聯繫我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年塔矢名人的兒子也來參加考試
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 今年我們的形勢更嚴峻了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是第幾次參加考試了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別提了 今年再考不上的話我就放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算輸了第一場比賽也無所謂嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是氣死人了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔矢亮呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是以職業棋手為目標而一直努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是經過了多少的艱辛才進入這個考場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼可能會明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 現在請開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 進藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天雨下得好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 一會兒再跟你打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【GoGo】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.71,0:22:11.90,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go Go 圍棋教室
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.73,0:22:12.31,gogo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(411,380)}梅澤由香裏的{\c&H0000FF&}GoGo{\r}圍棋教室
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:14.06,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H1C79E0&}{\bord2}{\pos(270,362)}{\fs28}由香裏老師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:14.79,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們今天繼續討論「眼」的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:16.89,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2}{\pos(322,392)}{\fs25}{\1c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&HFF0000&}優希                                                                  {\3c&HFF00FF&}{\1c&HFFFFFF&} 真唯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:16.89,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H008000&}{\1c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord3}{\pos(320,375)}{\fs25}繼續討論「眼」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:16.84,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這三個棋型中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:19.90,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H008000&}{\1c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord3}{\pos(304,380)}{\fs22}三個棋型看起來都有2個「眼」…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.94,0:22:19.19,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個無論怎麼下黑子都不會被提掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.26,0:22:20.58,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪一個呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:21.65,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.84,0:22:22.31,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.08,0:22:29.55,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真唯選的這個棋型確實有兩個「眼」所以不會被提掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.63,0:22:31.06,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:32.45,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管這裏看上去是個「眼」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:34.67,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可白子下在這裏還是會被提掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:37.32,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 這個棋型只有一個「眼」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.49,0:22:38.67,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:40.95,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是優希選的這個棋型
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.11,0:22:42.96,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏看上去是個「眼」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:45.18,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但白子下在這裏就會被提掉3子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:47.33,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也只剩下一個「眼」了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:52.18,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H008000&\pos(309,341)}{\1c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord3}{\fs22}看起來像「眼」卻不是「眼」的棋型叫做「假眼」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.33,0:22:51.98,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣看上去像「眼」但不是「眼」的就叫做「假眼」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.77,0:22:55.22,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H0000C8&\pos(327,372)}{\1c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord3}{\pos(320,370)}{\fs24}「眼」{\3c&H008000&}和{\3c&H0000C8&}「假眼」{\3c&H008000&}要注意區分!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.12,0:22:54.30,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「假眼」是很重要的知識點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:55.41,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要牢牢地記住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:56.48,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:57.35,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(500,390)}{\3c&H0000FF&}{\bord2}待續…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【下回預告】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:23:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了一個很厲害的棋手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.34,0:23:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫sai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.16,0:23:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於sai的真實身份引起了很大的爭論
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.97,0:23:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺到了比起進藤擊敗我時更強大的高牆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用這一手破壞掉白子的眼形!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.13,0:23:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰?

